# Helm And Kubernetes

- Use real dcgm-exporter flags from `pkg/cmd/app.go` in Helm `arguments`.
- Keep values, templates, raw YAML, and README examples aligned.
- RBAC changes must match the Kubernetes feature being enabled.
- Keep service read/write timeouts coherent with ServiceMonitor scrape
  timeout/interval.
- Document GPU/Kubernetes prerequisites for e2e validation.
